ygData.messageBody:
Has anyone found a note that had runes on it? I read in another post that
someone found one and the runes were very similar to the ones on the
Gnomish Clock in Qeynos. (I'm trying to determine where he might have
found this note) Perhaps if these runes could be deciphered, they might
lead to a clue to tinkering a collapsable fishing rod. Anyone notice
these runes anywhere else? Perhaps somewhere in Ak'anon?

Quasinom de Plume
